{"tid":1532702,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你地有無諗過可能會面對更恐怖嘅對待","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:33:17.000Z","uid":49898,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aff3cd04bf564f2977dc03da86b7ea2f3f772984","tid":1532702,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"運動去到依家，我地面對嘅不公平不公義嘅對待已經去到好嚴重<br />\n黑警：亂打人 私刑 性侵犯 （可能強姦）（可能殺死市民）<br />\n鄉黑、藍屍：亂打人 斬人 非禮<br />\n<br />\n而家都已經咁癲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但根據破窗效應，而佢地做嘅野係無後果<br />\n事情發展落去其實好大可能會更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n魔警隨意捉人打，捉返狗屋私刑性侵<br />\n大量愛國分子、中國人係街隨意殺人放火，姦淫擄掠<br />\n<br />\n我希望只係我想像力太豐富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔希望會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天佑真香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 到時你唔可以再有道德底線，因為你同身邊人都可能會受到慘痛經歷甚至死亡"},{"pid":"3e319d41ade7575c181708e412de23fd4fb453b3","tid":1532702,"uid":61002,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"預咗"},{"pid":"ffc75c63b80bb7e7a101f1757395892194ff0859","tid":1532702,"uid":49898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3e319d41ade7575c181708e412de23fd4fb453b3","tid":1532702,"uid":61002,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"預咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:04:47.000Z","msg":"我唔覺得好多香港人有"},{"pid":"f35ae77d614dbf18c87d63ef1a887e56d76fa612","tid":1532702,"uid":262190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"麻木我地，令沉默變成大多數人嘅選擇，應該就係佢地嘅手法之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw唔好意思阻阻你，可唔可以幫手諗下？<br />\n[全民BLACK BLOC日] The Most Legal Way Against White Terror<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532614</a>"},{"pid":"